<L>__{ext rubbish tip dawn}
<A>__{the morning light suffuses mountains of domestic refuse. rubbish for as far as the eye can see. plastic sacks of various colours, many spilling open. a few fires are burning. flocks of scavenging sea gulls hover and dive, screaming blue murder. on one of the many pinnacles of garbage sits a lonely figure. it's anton, depressed, angry, forlorn. the camera swings round to show, below anton, in a valley of waste material, the wagon.}
